AUDIO: 'Yesterday was the last day of the rest of our lives. Yesterday was the day Sam Olman asked his ego this three-word question. What have we done? Because yesterday was the day the human intelligence monopoly officially ended with the long-awaited release of OpenAI\'s GPT5, the first AI model to'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
