AUDIO: 'outperform biological humans on the Simple Bench benchmark. Meanwhile, it\'s quickly overtaking virtually every leaderboard on LM Marina, which means every programmer that still has a job will be getting a layoff notice shortly.'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Or at least that\'s what the hype engineers at OpenAI want you to think. Not everybody is falling for it, though. That simple bench score was just a rumor. And in fact, GPT5 is actually in fifth place. GPT5 failed to beat Grock on the ARC AGI benchmark, an important'

