VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'user needing to think about it. In many ways, GPT5 feels more like a consolidation and cost reduction effort after they spent the last year panic shipping a bunch of stupidly named models to justify the $200 pro plan. Speaking of cost though, GPT5 is priced'

